  Shirley looked glamorous as she rocked up to the red carpet wearing a matching white blazer and trouser set. The dancer wore a sparkling, semi-transparent top underneath that revealed part of her black bra. She completed the look with a silver necklace, large hoop earrings and some black stiletto heels. Danny looked dapper in a black tuxedo as he grinned while posing with his arm in a sling.  